description:
Pre-Pre-Alpha release from FourDeltaOne and Teknogods. 

You can enjoy playing Black Ops II Multiplayer or Zombies with your friends.

The torrent contains:

# Original Skidrow Release (don't download it if you already have it) and step by step instructions on how to install the game.

# Required updates

# All the DLC-s that are available at the moment


Just in case I'll post the instructions here:

Please note that this is a PRE-PRE-Alpha release! There are no dedicated servers for now! But you can play with the &quot;friends&quot; you add on(read the instructions below)

Even though this is a Pre-Pre-Alpha release, it is quite stable and the game runs smoothly!


1. Install &quot;Black.Ops.II-SKIDR*W&quot; 

2. Install &quot;Update #3&quot; and Copy and Replace the files from &quot;Skidrow&quot; folder to the 

main install folder

3. Copy and Replace the Files from &quot;Update #4&quot; folder to the main install folder

4. Copy and Replace the Files from &quot;T6M Pre-Pre-Alpha&quot; to the main install folder

5. Copy and Replace the Files from &quot;NukeTown &amp; Revolution DLC Pack&quot; to the main 

install folder 

6. Copy and Replace the Files from &quot;Uprising DLC Pack&quot; to the main install folder

7. Copy and Replace the Files from &quot;Vengeance DLC Pack&quot; to the main install folder

8. Copy and Replace the Files from &quot;OP2-T6M-DLC 3&quot; to the main install folder

9. Go toand make an account, add your friends

10. When you run either &quot;t6mp.exe&quot; (multiplayer) or &quot;t6mz&quot; (zombies) for the first 

time, you'll have to fill in your FourDeltaOne Username and password!

11. Enjoy the game :))

NOTE: You MAY or MAY NOT get some errors from time to time:
# Run the game &quot;as an administrator&quot;
# IF you get the error &quot;t6mp.exe&quot; (Black Ops II multiplayer) or &quot;t6zm&quot; (Black Ops II zombies) stopped working when you run the game, keep calm, 
close the game and run again (once or twice) until it starts normally

Big thanks to the people at Teknogods and Fourdeltaone who made this awesome release!

Seed and Enjoy! :))

